prompt: A luxurious living room bathed in natural light from large windows and doors, showcasing Moroccan-style floor textures. The room features white walls, with an Arabic calligraphy decoration on one wall, complementing the intricate wooden ceiling beams. A patterned rug serves as the centerpiece of the seating area, flanked by multiple couches and a bench adorned with colorful pillows. On the right side of the room, a dining table set for six is visible, with a basket weave over it adding to the rustic charm. The overall aesthetic is one of elegance and warmth, combining traditional elements with modern comforts.
